5 and f <sigma v> / m = 1/100 picobarn c / GeV, we can limit\nthe mass variance sigma_{max} < 100 at the 95% confidence level, corresponding\nto a power law index m_s < 1.43 (1.63) for k_p = 100 (1000) h/Mpc. Our results\nare also relevant to theories that feature a running spectral index.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2015 20:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-13"}
