red to overcome the stellar feedback\nto form the high-mass star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2015 00:43:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 2015 14:06:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
